cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with learning representations for semantic relations between words. It could also belong to "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes an unsupervised method for learning vector representations for words. Additionally, it could be categorized under "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the proposed method could be useful for relation classification in text retrieval systems. Finally, it could also be categorized under "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the proposed method involves training a binary classifier.
